---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import settings from '../content/singletons/settings.json';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility | Morning Light Counseling"
  description="Morning Light Counseling's commitment to an accessible website for all visitors."
>
  <PageHero title="Accessibility" />

  <article class="prose-ml mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-16 text-lg sm:px-6">
    <p>
      Morning Light Counseling wants every man who needs help to be able to find it — including visitors who use
      screen readers, keyboard navigation, or other assistive technology.
    </p>

    <h2>What this site does</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Built to meet <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> guidelines</li>
      <li>Full keyboard navigation, with a visible focus indicator and a skip-to-content link</li>
      <li>Text and background colors chosen for sufficient contrast</li>
      <li>Meaningful alternative text on images and properly structured headings and landmarks</li>
      <li>Respects your system's reduced-motion preference</li>
      <li>Readable and usable at 200% zoom and on screens of any size</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Found a problem?</h2>
    <p>
      If any part of this site is difficult for you to use, please say so — it will get fixed. Email
      {settings.email} or call {settings.phone}, and if the website is the barrier, we're glad to handle scheduling
      entirely by phone.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
